Name: Cookie Clicker but You Type
About the game: Cookie Clicker but You Type brings typing to the addictive incremental style of a certain cookie-earning game. Upgrades can be purchased with keys, and are used to help the player gain keys faster. Additionally, there is a race mode which allows players to time themselves as they race to earn 10,000 keys!
